@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'İş süreçleri'
define view entity ykpi_i_business_processes
  as select from    ykpi_t_process  as BusinessProcesses
    left outer join ykpi_t_processx as Description on  Description.language               = $session.system_language
                                                   and BusinessProcesses.main_module      = Description.main_module
                                                   and BusinessProcesses.business_process = Description.business_process
  association to parent ykpi_i_main_modules as _mainModules on $projection.MainModule = _mainModules.MainModule
  composition [1..*] of ykpi_i_data_sources as _dataSources
{
  key BusinessProcesses.main_module      as MainModule,
  key BusinessProcesses.business_process as BusinessProcess,
      Description.description            as Description,
      _mainModules,
      _dataSources
}
